      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZELDA COVILHA (4) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (30.44) in a OPEN at Angle Park. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Top chance in this line up. RALPH WIGGUM (2) scored an upset win in a Mix 3/4 at this track last time in the best time of the card (29.90). Has a good record here including two wins. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. HIGHLY CONNECTED (6) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fourth and beaten 4 lengths (30.62) at Angle Park. Has a good record here at this journey. Likely to be about the money. PAW DAMON (8) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
